Package org.cpnsim.datacenter

Class InstanceQueueFifo

java.lang.Object
org.cpnsim.datacenter.InstanceQueueFifo
All Implemented Interfaces:
InstanceQueue
public class InstanceQueueFifo extends Object implements InstanceQueue
A class to represent a instance queue with first in first out. This class implements the interface InstanceQueue.
Since:
CPNSim 1.0
Author:
Jiawen Liu
